						<div class="elementskit-single-testimonial-slider elementskit-testimonial-slider-block-style  elementor-repeater-item-a709f36">
							<div class="elementskit-commentor-bio client_left">
																<span class="elementskit-profile-info">
									<strong class="elementskit-author-name">Mr. Abhishek Sharma Parent of Daivik Sharma, Class - 4th C</strong>
									<span class="elementskit-author-des"></span>
								</span>
							</div>
							<div class="elementskit-commentor-content">
																	
									<span class="elementskit-watermark-icon ekit_watermark_icon_custom_position">
																			</span>

																									<p>The whole SMSL event was so good and so well managed and it was really a very proud moment to see our kid performing and learning with such a wonderful team of teachers.</p>
